item.title: Getting Started with Github Pages
item.description: 1What is Github Pages? 2How to make your home page When you use GitHub pages, you can access your website at the url http://username.github.io and the underlying files would be found in your repository, which can be found at url pattern ttp://github.

item.title: Getting started with Git
item.description: 1Git Version control systems are used in managing revision control of project artifacts, and maintaining a history of changes to each artifact. Artifacts can include documents, source code, and much more.
